---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Implementation | Cody Smith" description="CRM integrations, page builds, analytics setup. Scoped projects with a start and a finish.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative pt-40 pb-24 px-6 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/3 w-[600px] h-[400px] bg-amber-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <a href="/services" class="reveal inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-neutral-500 text-sm hover:text-neutral-300 transition-colors duration-300 mb-8 group">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 16l-4-4m0 0l4-4m-4 4h18" />
        </svg>
        All services
      </a>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <span class="reveal text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.2em]">03</span>
        <div class="reveal gradient-divider flex-1"></div>
      </div>
      <h1 class="reveal font-serif text-5xl md:text-7xl text-neutral-100 leading-[1.05] mb-6">
        Implementation
      </h1>
      <p class="reveal text-neutral-500 italic text-sm tracking-wide mb-10">Changes to production systems.</p>
      <p class="reveal text-neutral-400 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        Your forms don't connect to your CRM. Your analytics are either broken or lying. You need pages that don't exist yet. These gaps cost you leads and visibility. I scope the fix, quote it, build it, and hand it over.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Project types -->
  <section class="py-28 px-6 surface-1">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="reveal mb-16">
        <p class="text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4">Project types</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl text-neutral-100">What I build.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8 reveal-stagger">
        <div class="reveal glow-card p-8" style="--i:0">
          <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="lg:col-span-2">
              <h3 class="text-neutral-100 text-xl font-medium mb-4">Integrations</h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Your forms submit but nothing happens on the other end. Leads don't reach your CRM. Email sequences never fire. Payment confirmations vanish. The connections between your site and your business tools are either broken or missing entirely.
              </p>
              <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
                I build those connections. Form submissions that land in your CRM. Email sequences that trigger when someone downloads a guide. Payment links that actually track conversions.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l border-white/5 pl-8">
              <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mb-4">Common projects</p>
              <ul class="text-neutral-300 text-sm space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1.5 text-[8px]">&#9670;</span>
                  Gravity Forms → Pipedrive
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1.5 text-[8px]">&#9670;</span>
                  Brevo email automation
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1.5 text-[8px]">&#9670;</span>
                  WooCommerce + payment
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1.5 text-[8px]">&#9670;</span>
                  Custom webhook flows
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal glow-card p-8" style="--i:1">
          <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="lg:col-span-2">
              <h3 class="text-neutral-100 text-xl font-medium mb-4">Page builds</h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Landing pages, service pages, content rewrites. The pages that need to exist for your marketing to work. Built to convert, optimized for search, written for humans.
              </p>
              <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
                I handle everything from keyword-targeted content architecture to the actual build in WordPress. You review, approve, and it goes live.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l border-white/5 pl-8">
              <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mb-4">Common projects</p>
              <ul class="text-neutral-300 text-sm space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1.5 text-[8px]">&#9670;</span>
                  Location landing pages
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1.5 text-[8px]">&#9670;</span>
                  Service/product pages
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1.5 text-[8px]">&#9670;</span>
                  Homepage rewrites
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1.5 text-[8px]">&#9670;</span>
                  Pricing pages
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal glow-card p-8" style="--i:2">
          <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="lg:col-span-2">
              <h3 class="text-neutral-100 text-xl font-medium mb-4">Analytics setup</h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Most sites have analytics installed. Very few have analytics configured correctly. Your GA4 might be running, but if events, conversions, and filters aren't set up right, the data is just noise.
              </p>
              <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
                I configure GA4, Google Search Console, Microsoft Clarity, and conversion tracking so the numbers you see actually mean something.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l border-white/5 pl-8">
              <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mb-4">Common projects</p>
              <ul class="text-neutral-300 text-sm space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1.5 text-[8px]">&#9670;</span>
                  GA4 configuration
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1.5 text-[8px]">&#9670;</span>
                  Search Console setup
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1.5 text-[8px]">&#9670;</span>
                  Conversion tracking
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1.5 text-[8px]">&#9670;</span>
                  Cookie consent compliance
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How projects work -->
  <section class="py-28 px-6 dot-grid">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="reveal mb-16">
        <p class="text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4">Process</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl text-neutral-100">How projects work.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 reveal-stagger">
        <div class="reveal glow-card p-6 text-center" style="--i:0">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-amber-500 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-amber-400 text-sm font-mono font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-neutral-100 font-medium mb-2">Scope</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">You describe what you need. I define exactly what's included, what's not, and what it costs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal glow-card p-6 text-center" style="--i:1">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-amber-500/70 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-amber-400/70 text-sm font-mono font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-neutral-100 font-medium mb-2">Quote</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Fixed price. No hourly surprises. You approve the quote, pay at signing, and work begins.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal glow-card p-6 text-center" style="--i:2">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-amber-500/50 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-amber-400/50 text-sm font-mono font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-neutral-100 font-medium mb-2">Build</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">I build it. You get progress updates. If something changes scope, we discuss it before the price changes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal glow-card p-6 text-center" style="--i:3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-amber-500/30 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-amber-400/30 text-sm font-mono font-bold">4</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-neutral-100 font-medium mb-2">Deliver</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">You review, I revise if needed, it goes live. Documentation included so your team knows what changed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing note -->
  <section class="py-28 px-6 surface-1">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4">Pricing</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl text-neutral-100 mb-8">Project-based pricing.</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Implementation work is quoted per-project, not billed hourly. The scope defines the price.
        </p>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Rate card for reference: <span class="text-neutral-200">$125/hr</span> implementation, <span class="text-neutral-200">$150/hr</span> advisory. Rush work is <span class="text-neutral-200">1.5x</span>. Emergency is <span class="text-neutral-200">2x</span>.
        </p>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm">
          Most projects are scoped at a fixed price so you know the cost before work begins.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="relative py-32 px-6 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[500px] h-[300px] bg-amber-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="reveal font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl text-neutral-100 mb-6">Have a project in mind?</h2>
      <p class="reveal text-neutral-400 text-lg mb-10">Tell me what needs to happen and I'll tell you what it takes.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="reveal inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-amber-500 text-neutral-950 font-semibold text-sm rounded-lg hover:bg-amber-400 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(245,158,11,0.25)]">
        Start a conversation
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
